    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337780/extras/f8a4f65b29f6ed6d8bbb0b2bd011c666.avif?t=1741803572\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump &amp; Hook 的核心玩法很简单——用你的钩索攀爬向上！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用惯性摆荡跃升，巧妙借助地形缠绕绳索，探索无数种冲顶方式！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump &amp; Hook 是一款精准平台跳跃类 2D 单人游戏，你将操控一名装备钩索的小机器人，通过钩索勾住物体，在环境间反弹、左右摆动，并猛力弹射向上！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别忘了把游戏加入愿望清单！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要小心，松开钩索的时机至关重要——如果判断失误，目标落空，你会直接坠落！游戏没有存档点，但如果够快，你仍然可以在下落途中抓住物体，绝地求生！  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br>目标</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标是登顶！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含 5 个不同的关卡，你需要逐一闯关，证明自己真正掌握了钩索技巧。每个关卡都会带来新的挑战，需要你动脑解决，例如利用物体缠绕绳索、仅能从上方勾住等。   <br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br>自由度</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供了极高的自由度，你可以自行探索最优路线，不断优化攀爬策略，挑战更快纪录！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祝你好运！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337780/extras/32c249debba64adc45d9f338d03b5d99.poster.avif?t=1741803572\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337780/extras/32c249debba64adc45d9f338d03b5d99.webm?t=1741803572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337780/extras/32c249debba64adc45d9f338d03b5d99.mp4?t=1741803572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
